 never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/evcohen/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/master/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","JSXOpeningElement","react/jsx-no-duplicate-props","No duplicate props allowed","JSXAttribute","'theType' is defined but never used.","'AllCities' is defined but never used.","'getState' is assigned a value but never used.","jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","'useContext' is defined but never used.","The 'changeHandler' function makes the dependencies of useEffect Hook (at line 37) change on every render. To fix this, wrap the definition of 'changeHandler' in its own useCallback() Hook.","VariableDeclarator",["294"],"no-native-reassign",["295"],"no-negated-in-lhs",["296"],["297"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'filter'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["298"],["299"],"'Link' is defined but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'search'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["300"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'search.sellOrRent'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["301"],{"desc":"302","fix":"303"},{"desc":"304","fix":"305"},"no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation",{"desc":"302","fix":"306"},{"desc":"307","fix":"308"},{"desc":"307","fix":"309"},{"desc":"310","fix":"311"},{"desc":"312","fix":"313"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [id]",{"range":"314","text":"315"},"Wrap the definition of 'changeHandler' in its own useCallback() Hook.",{"range":"316","text":"317"},{"range":"318","text":"315"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [filter]",{"range":"31